          <h3 class="project-title font-display">Guardian Phonebook</h3>
        </a>

        <p class="project-desc">
          Modern internal employee directory replacing a legacy static HTML
          phonebook. Features a public directory, admin dashboard, and scheduled
          LDAP sync — built with Keycloak SSO and deployed in production at
          Guardian Life Insurance Ltd.
        </p>

        <div class="project-tags">
          <a
            href="https://nextjs.org/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="tag"
